3.27.213:50051: i/o timeout`\n     - 日志中出现了 `timed out waiting for server handshake`\n     - 日志中出现了 `rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error`\n   - **Reason**: 这些日志指示系统在尝试连接远程服务时遇到网络超时问题。这通常与网络配置问题或高负载状态有关。\n   - **Component**: 服务名 `frontend` (涉及多次连接失败的服务)\n\n2. **请求取消**:\n   - **Evidence**:\n     - 日志中出现了 `rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled`\n   - **Reason**: 指示某些请求由于长时间未响应而被客户端或服务器取消。这可能是由于网络延迟过高导致请求最终被放弃。\n   - **Component**: 服务名 `frontend`\n\n基于这些关键信息，可以推测出问题的发生可能是由于 `frontend` 服务从未能有效地与某个远程服务进行网络交互（包括网络连接的超时及封锁）。这种情况可能源于网络配置、负载过高或远程服务不可用等因素。\n\n如下是规模及频次最大的错误日志片段：\n- 日志内容: `\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.27.213:50051: i/o timeout\"`\n- 出现次数: 47\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"rpc error\", \"context canceled\", \"timed out\", \"i/o timeout\", \"transport\", \"Error while dialing\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Network timeout and connection errors during remote service communication\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Logging info like 'transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.27.213:50051: i/o timeout'\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Requests being canceled probably due to excessive delay\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Code = Canceled desc = context canceled logs\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n建议进一步调查网络拓扑结构和远程服务的可用性。", "metric_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"memory_usage\",\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"server_error_ratio\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"rrt_max\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tidb\",\n      \"reason\": \"The memory usage of tidb-tidb increased by 12.59% as the median memory usage moved from 649,756,672 to 737,087,488.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"memory_usage exceeds normal with a median change ratio of 0.1259.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingserv